Usage: unfixBump [-help] {-allBumps  | -byBumpName <bump1 bump2...>}

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-allBumps                        # removes the bump assignment status from all
                                 # bumps (bool, required)
-byBumpName <bump1 bump2...>     # removes the bump assignment status from a
                                 # specified list of assigned bumps
                                 # (string, required)